Z","msg":"一來島仔太細，二來葡佬又膽細，三來果陣共匪識玩"},{"pid":"aa5e9a0fb9dca31b5878b9f6eb42e6858e80989c","tid":1788331,"uid":83713,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T16:22:12.000Z","msg":"葡萄牙帝國真係好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你睇邊個葡國殖民地富得起來先得架"},{"pid":"34ef783269f010d1333bf6129f7aa344b126d1b3","tid":1788331,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T16:24:10.000Z","msg":"跪求所有行動POST <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和你推</span></span><br />\n我要成個時事台都係呢個行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日國際線行動要人阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[求置頂][推行動] 19/12 社福界搞人權法請願遊行(下午) + 集會(晚上)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1787706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1787706</a><br />\n<br />\n突發！國際線同罷工戰線要人，咁重要既行動都冇人講！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1788283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1788283</a><br />\n<br />\n［打錯日子重開］聽日1219有九國領事館遊行！夜晚仲有集會！無人知？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1788267\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1788267</a>"},{"pid":"6b2d73a7ff5e0c60d2baa9a7fb7559cf028ae49d","tid":1788331,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T16:34:47.000Z","msg":"你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4b04eb5114e1719d2824007a53ff3366f28e4c","tid":1788331,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T00:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gi